<%= @greeting %>
Thank you for booking on Flight <%= @booking.flight.flight_number %> on <%= @booking.flight.airline.name %> airlines.

Please visit <%= booking_url(@booking) %> to view your booking.

Your confirmation number is <%= rand(100000..999999) %>

You are flying from <%= @booking.flight.origin_airport.name %> to <%= @booking.flight.destination_airport.name %>

Departure date: <%= @booking.flight.departure_time.strftime("%b %d, %Y") %>
Departure time: <%= @booking.flight.departure_time.strftime("%l:%M %P")%>
<% arrival_time = @booking.flight.departure_time + @booking.flight.duration.minutes %>
Arrival time: <%= arrival_time.strftime("%l:%M %P")%>
<% hours = @booking.flight.duration / 60 %>
<% minutes = @booking.flight.duration % 60 %>
Flight Duration: <%= "#{hours}:#{minutes}" %>

Passengers:
<% @booking.passengers.each do |passenger|%>
  <%= passenger.passenger_name %> Email: <%= passenger.passenger_email %>
<% end %>
